TextChange: Sometimes we try to create an  impression by saying or creating something but others perceive it in other way . In this situation it is better to remain silent. Impression or images are not the important factors. I does not determines our behavior. Only our actions that reflect our thought and decide what type of person we are. Only our true values will prove us to this world.
